  "title": "Aurelia Support?",
  "body": "I've been trying unsuccessfully to get instantsearch.js to integrate with the Aurelia (http://aurelia.io) library.  One of the committers for the Aurelia CLI said that instantsearch.js was particularly tricky and asked me to open an issue so they could investigate further. https://github.com/aurelia/cli/issues/593 \r\n\r\nIs there any example of how to integrate it or would it be possible to provide support for Aurelia?\r\n\r\nThanks",
